518
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:25,800
I'll take care of it myself. I'll take care of it.

519
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:28,600
It's fine! Something fell down just now.

520
00:38:28,600 --> 00:38:30,100
Who replaced him?

521
00:38:30,100 --> 00:38:32,000
Huikang's Engineer Liu.

522
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:35,800
Engineer Liu?

523
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:38,700
He came to our company during the O&T testing last time.

524
00:38:38,700 --> 00:38:41,000
I got it.

525
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,580
Hello, Director Zhou!

526
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:12,500
You must make sure that our bidding document is safe.

527
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:16,000
I'm guarding it. Tomorrow, I'll escort the car to the resort village.

528
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:19,300
Ever since you were a kid, as soon as you interfere, something will be missing from here or there.

529
00:39:19,300 --> 00:39:21,300
- Wait a moment!
