534
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:38,600
I was talking to Grandma.

535
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:43,800
One of the stakes that we planted

536
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:45,600
has been pulled by Huikang.

537
00:39:45,600 --> 00:39:48,540
Hence, we have only one method now,

538
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:50,500
change the bid!

539
00:39:51,950 --> 00:39:54,260
Change the bid?

540
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:58,690
Fang Wei, listen!

541
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:02,400
